        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Strengthening Social Connections Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill provides FY2021 supplemental appropriations to the Administration for Community Living for various activities to address the health effects of extended social isolation and loneliness among older individuals due to factors such as the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
